they are able to enter the presence of @wDN{Utu}, of @wDN{Enlil}, god of the ……, the bearded son of @wDN{Ningal} ……; they give to @wDN{Suen} ……, they confirm with their power the fate of the foreign lands. At dead of night they know the black wild boar, at midday to @wDN{Utu} …… he can …… his incantation,
