@(A.485 = 485-499) As @wDN{Utu} comes forth from his chamber, the holy battle-mace of @wDN{An} ……, the just god who lies alongside a man; they are wicked gods with evil hearts, they are …… gods. It is they, like @wDN{Nanna}, like @wDN{Utu}, like @wDN{Inana} of the fifty divine powers, …… in heaven and earth ……; they are the interpreters of spoken evil, the spies of righteousness,
